<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Confirm your new order <%=raw @seller.id%> at www.coincompass.net</h1>
    <p>
      You have recently submitted a new sell order at www.coincompass.net. Please review the details below and confirm they are correct.
    </p>
    Bank Name   <%=@seller.bank_name.present? ? @seller.bank_name : @seller.credname %>
    Account Name  <%=@seller.bank_name.present? ? @seller.bank_name : @seller.credname %>
    Account Number  <%=@seller.seller_account_number%>
    Amount of BTC to sell <%=@seller.sell_amount%>
    To modify or cancel your order, go to this page, enter your order modification PIN and confirm.
    To view pending buyer holds and the status of your order, go to this page.
    Please finalise your order by sending 5 BTC to the below address, and your order will be placed live after 1 confirmation:

    <span><%= raw @seller.bit_address %></span>
    <span><%=image_tag attachments['missing.png'].url %></span>
  </body>
</html>